    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>--Solution 1</strong> : Go to : <strong>window</strong> &gt; <strong>preferences</strong> &gt; <strong>java</strong> &gt; <strong>Editor</strong> &gt; <strong>mark occurrences</strong> and disable : <strong>mark occurrences ...</strong></p>\n<p><strong>--Solution 2 (deeply recommended)</strong> : if you need to use <strong>mark occurences</strong>, use <strong>eclipse 2022-12 and this will fix the error</strong>. Then choose the type of ide that you want, if you use JEE dowload <strong>Eclipse IDE for Enterprise Java and Web Developers 2022-12</strong></p>\n"
