      "body" : "Unfortunately, by removing the indicated file, the Help-&gt;&quot;Eclipse Marketplace...&quot; option disappeared, although the problem was resolved. Re-entering the file didn&#39;t fix it, I had to reinstall Eclipse. Personally, I do <b>not</b> recommend this method."
