    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I'm using eclipse version 2022-06, and ran into this same problem.</p>\n<p>I just updated the pluggins and IDE, and it solved itself.</p>\n<p>At the top bar menu, go to,\n<strong>Help &gt; Check For Updates</strong></p>\n"
